snippet.title: [Super Monkey Ball Banana Rumble] SEGA PASS Character Introduction: Sonic, Tails, Amy, Knuckles
snippet.description:
Super Monkey Ball Banana Rumble will be launching exclusively on Nintendo Switch on June 25, 2024!
https://asia.sega.com/bananarumble/en/

Pre-order today 🐵
https://asia.sega.com/bananarumble/en/guide.html

Introducing Sonic, Tails, Amy, and Knuckles, four of the six characters that will appear in Sega Pass!

#SMB #SuperMonkeyBall #BananaRumble #SEGA
